IIRC, you folks are part of the VS rotation as well as the Trak rotation, so I don't see what makes this any different.  For those (Kunark) mobs, you are not committed to an FFA society because you do follow the rotation <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> .  I could be wrong here as I do NOT follow whos turn it is for Trak: I just show up when our turn is on and participate.<br>
