<br>
I did make a pitch on our message boards prior to reading here this evening, so I should have some feedback in a day or two.<br>
<br>
I was unaware of Rage despawning.  This does create some problems.  I will need to get some more background on this, but a per rotation basis does aleviate this issue to some extent.  This then becomes very similar to the Trak rotation solution.<br>
<br>
I understand the concerns about clerics needing to be a specific level (from the lottery solution attempted previously).  By using a guild rotation, the guilds handle whose turn it is for Rage (within the guild).<br>
<br>
Nice to see some of the other guilds chiming in here and at least open to discussion.  Lets keep it civil and try to come up with a workable deal. <p>Tanuden <BR>
